{"sections":{"main":{"blocks":[{"value":{"height":"200","url":"\/-content\/icing\/icon_256x256@2x.png?v=2","width":"200","description":"Icing icon"},"typeGroup":"media","type":"externalImage","identifier":"i-5246262939181179"},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"heading","identifier":"i-4270160160958767","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-9977706880308688","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Icing"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-4679662596900016","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-915919782128185","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Icing lets you create content: articles, blog posts, or about pages. It is available now to use online, and soon as a dedicated app for the Mac."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"subhead1","identifier":"i-6641330854035914","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-2208489398472011","type":"text","traits":{"link":{"typeChoice":{"URL":{"URL":"\/icing\/use\/"}}},"class":{"classNames":"primaryLink"}},"text":"Use Online for Free"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"subhead1","identifier":"i-19094125810079277","textItems":[{"text":"Benefits: no more markup","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-5909153346437961"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-23746242513880134","textItems":[{"text":"Icing doesn’t require a language like HTML or Markdown to be learned. ","type":"text","traits":{"bold":false},"identifier":"i-7970702068414539"},{"text":"Both HTML and Markdown require a syntax — a juggling of characters around what you’re actually writing — in order to add formatting and structure. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-9739535960834473"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-4441331038251519","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-002986427629366517","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"This includes things like making text bold or italic, adding links or images or interactive elements, or are clearly identified to be worked onto the page in a particular way."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-27136565558612347","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-8191033096518368","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Icing is a visual editor. But one you may not be used to. "}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-9079991125036031","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-5026467037387192","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Apps like Microsoft Word or WordPress can be referred to by the strange term "},{"identifier":"i-7725950300227851","type":"text","traits":{"italic":true},"text":"What You See Is What You Get"},{"identifier":"i-8787055315915495","type":"text","traits":{},"text":". "},{"identifier":"i-81524349283427","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"While you can see the final result in front of your eyes, the only problem is you often get only basic formatting. "},{"identifier":"i-20507434848695993","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"If you want to do something more elaborate you either have to delve into HTML or you become stuck, unable to make what you like."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-22890478116460145","textItems":[{"text":"Icing has a rich structure like HTML whilst being much easier to use. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-5823140202555805"},{"text":"It also has a visual preview that shows a fair representation of what your content will look like to a reader.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-8987095693591982"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-6639284810516983","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-41904707811772823","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Content in Icing is flexible using little pieces of text all strung together. "},{"identifier":"i-761142329312861","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Each piece can have "},{"identifier":"i-07667220290750265","type":"text","traits":{"italic":true},"text":"traits"},{"identifier":"i-7191298599354923","type":"text","traits":{},"text":", like whether the text is bold or italic, or if it has a link. "},{"identifier":"i-54328050930053","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Pretty much any small bit of info can be attached to a piece of text."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-05566198076121509","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-02222501370124519","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"You could call it a "},{"identifier":"i-08217177493497729","type":"text","traits":{"link":{"typeChoice":{"URL":{"URL":"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/WYSIWYM"}}},"italic":true},"text":"What You See Is What You Mean"},{"identifier":"i-835288678528741","type":"text","traits":{},"text":" editor if you wanted a strange name for it too."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"subhead1","identifier":"i-13464318006299436","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-12567264935933053","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Open Source"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-3083793190307915","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-6039587478153408","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"The Icing Editor is open source on GitHub: "},{"identifier":"i-3013668302446604","type":"text","traits":{"link":{"typeChoice":{"URL":{"URL":"https:\/\/github.com\/BurntIcing\/IcingEditor"}}}},"text":"https:\/\/github.com\/BurntIcing\/IcingEditor"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-9516378571279347","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-9388191311154515","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"A library for displaying Icing files on the web is also available for PHP: "},{"identifier":"i-9913038639351726","type":"text","traits":{"link":{"typeChoice":{"URL":{"URL":"https:\/\/github.com\/BurntIcing\/IcingPHP"}}}},"text":"https:\/\/github.com\/BurntIcing\/IcingPHP"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"subhead1","identifier":"i-4879119119141251","textItems":[{"text":"Specs","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-6807960907462984"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-3317005673889071","textItems":[{"text":"Let experts create specs which have the different traits and elements that you need, and then put it together yourself. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-09613002114929259"},{"text":"Break a web page into distinct sections, each which can be set up in their own way: ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-33897631149739027"},{"text":"this is the main article, this is the introduction, this is a gallery.","type":"text","traits":{"italic":true},"identifier":"i-8524405816569924"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-48804869945161045","textItems":[{"text":"The content can be served on a website as is, or fully customised by a web developer. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-09929817775264382"},{"text":"Web developers can add whatever HTML attributes or CSS classes or JavaScript interactivity they like. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-2580025880597532"},{"text":"The best thing is the writer doesn’t have to worry themselves with those technicalities.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-368241484509781"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-7304728727322072","textItems":[{"text":"A spec could display a image slider, or show a summary of multiple items, or put footnotes at the bottom of the page, or add additional elements and attributes for better accessibility, or visibly show a link for printing, or create an RSS feed.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-8897781488485634"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-6318772158119828","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-842859699157998","type":"text","traits":{"link":{"typeChoice":{"URL":{"URL":"http:\/\/burnticing.github.io\/specs\/default\/1.0\/default-1.0.json"}}}},"text":"An example JSON spec can be viewed here."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"subhead1","identifier":"i-7046974536497146","textItems":[{"text":"The potential uses of Icing for writers, developers, and editors","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-9399827695451677"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","identifier":"i-5981560316868126","typeGroup":"subsection"},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-5510651194490492","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-22079027956351638","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Keeps basic content simple whilst also allowing more advanced elements. "},{"identifier":"i-1907839763443917","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Allow typos to be corrected, additions to be included, and customisations easily made by anyone without developer assistance."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-162868409184739","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-8981721447780728","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Interweave elements dynamically into the content of a web site, such as images, links, videos, or interactive JavaScript components."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-8976806767750531","textItems":[{"text":"Create static web pages: publish as flat HTML pages for speedy loading.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-11191598908044398"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-4425064269453287","textItems":[{"text":"Custom types: use ‘particular’ or ‘media’ blocks with fields to make customisable additions.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-03929480677470565"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-5236130675766617","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-8167669265531003","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Make multiple elements consistent across pages or sites, while keeping their arrangement, formatting, or punctuation controlled separately. "},{"identifier":"i-46010975376702845","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"Ideal for picky editors and web developers."}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-5853690677322447","textItems":[{"text":"HTML agnostic: Isn’t directly connected to HTML, so alternate methods of publishing are possible: RSS, SVG, plain text, Markdown, ebook, PDF. ","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-7767849166411906"},{"text":"Icing documents are JSON, so create whatever transformations you like.","type":"text","traits":{},"identifier":"i-7054212964139879"}]},{"typeGroup":"text","type":"body","identifier":"i-04064334533177316","textItems":[{"identifier":"i-5334390681236982","type":"text","traits":{},"text":"A simple format to convert into: hopefully to come will be tools to use Word, Excel, CSV, JSON and other file formats with Icing. These then could be published in the above formats, or dynamically processed in other ways."}]}]}}}